User "1" --> "0..*" PerformanceLog : logs
Game "0..1" --> "0..*" PerformanceLog : linked

User "1" --> "0..*" FriendRequest : requester
User "1" --> "0..*" FriendRequest : recipient
User "0..*" --> "0..*" User : friends

User "1" --> "0..*" Notification : receives
User "1" --> "0..*" RatingDismissal : dismisses
Game "1" --> "0..*" RatingDismissal

User "1" --> "0..*" SportCategory : creates

